  - m_Id: 2241531191296
    m_Localized: "<align=center><size=130%><color=#FFD700><b>~ RULES ~</b></color></size></align>\r\n\r\n<color=#FFD700><b>GAME
      OBJECTIVE</b></color>\r\nThe seer who ends the round with the <color=#50C878>lowest
      score</color> on their table, wins.\r\n\r\n<color=#FFD700><b>MYSTICAL POWERS</b></color>\r\nBy
      discarding these cards on your turn, you will unleash their magic:\r\n\r\n<color=#50C878><b>\u2022
      Cards 4 and 5:</b></color> Inner vision. Allows you to secretly look at one
      of your own hidden cards.\r\n<color=#50C878><b>\u2022 Cards 6 and 7:</b></color>
      Enemy vision. Allows you to spy on one of your opponent's hidden cards.\r\n<color=#50C878><b>\u2022
      The 10 (Jack):</b></color> The great exchange. Swap the position of one of
      your cards with one from your opponent.\r\n\r\n<color=#FFD700><b>LUCKY CARDS</b></color>\r\n<color=#50C878><b>\u2022
      The 12 (King) of Coins and Cups:</b></color> These sacred cards are worth exactly
      0 points!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
